<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM2.6.2">
<l>pārvaṇṇa maṭamaṅkai paṉinaṉmā malarkkiḻatti</l>
<l>nīrvaṇṇaṉ mārvakatti lirukkaiyaimuṉ niṉaintavaṉūr</l>
<l>kārvaṇṇa mutumunnīrk kaṭalmallait talacayaṉa</l>
<l>māreṇṇum neñcuṭaiyā ravaremmai yāḷvārē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Whoever has a heart which contemplates his city, Talacayaṉam</l>
<l>At Mallai by the sea, the ancient, dark-hued three-watered [ocean],</l>
<l rend="indent">having first reflected on</l>
<l>The simple maiden whose form is the earth and the mistress</l>
<l rend="indent">of the fine, great, dewy blossom</l>
<l>Sitting on the expanse of his sea-hued chest, they will rule over us.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
